      <title>Clearlake 支持的 Springs Window 试图联合竞争的债务集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/clearlake-backed-springs-window-seeks-to-unite-vying-debt-groups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Clearlake Capital Group 支持的 Springs Window Fashions LLC 正在与两个债权人集团进行谈判，寻求一项债务重组协议，以使两个最近争斗的派系都能参与其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/clearlake-backed-springs-window-seeks-to-unite-vying-debt-groups</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:58:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>糖业巨头 Cosan 考虑出售淡水河谷股份以应对杠杆问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/sugar-giant-cosan-mulls-selling-vale-stake-on-leverage-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁鲁本斯·奥梅托 (Rubens Ometto) 的企业集团 Cosan SA 正在考虑出售包括其在矿业巨头淡水河谷 (Vale SA) 持有的价值 22 亿美元的股份在内的资产，此举可能会解除一笔失败的赌注以偿还债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/sugar-giant-cosan-mulls-selling-vale-stake-on-leverage-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:56:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农作物贸易商 Olam 因延迟提交棉花销售报告被罚款 330 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/olam-to-pay-3-3-million-fine-for-delayed-cotton-sales-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农作物贸易商奥兰集团有限公司 (Olam Group Ltd.) 因延迟向美国农业部和商品期货交易委员会报告棉花销售情况，将支付 330 万美元罚款，此举可能会影响棉花价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/olam-to-pay-3-3-million-fine-for-delayed-cotton-sales-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Elliott 关联公司以 72.8 亿美元竞标成功赢得 Citgo 拍卖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/elliott-affiliate-wins-citgo-auction-with-7-28-billion-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 的一家附属公司在 Citgo Petroleum Corp. 母公司的拍卖中以 72.8 亿美元的出价成为领先竞标者，从而收购了曾是委内瑞拉最大海外资产的一家炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/elliott-affiliate-wins-citgo-auction-with-7-28-billion-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:39:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度放宽大米出口限制，为全球消费者提供缓冲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/india-eases-curbs-on-rice-exports-cushioning-global-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度放松了部分大米出口限制，此举可能缓解全球大米价格，并预示着最近全国大选后国内农业政策将发生转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/india-eases-curbs-on-rice-exports-cushioning-global-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:02:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
